                  <additions><!--THIS element in domlib CONTAINS ESCAPED HTML, thus it is not possible to reliably extract the information about pages. Please watch out.-->
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#">Fol. 1r: Unidentified prayer.</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#00">Fols. 1v-2r: Protective prayer.</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 1v: በእድጋድ፡ ወሰለለሎነ፡ ዑራኤል፡ ሰዱያልስ፡ ሰሰንያልስ፡ ተማምዖዶሙ፡ መድፍን፡ ድፍን፡ ልበሙ፡ ወእድልም፡ አዕይንቲሆሙ፡ አድከም፡ ኃይሎሙ፡...</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus target="#00">Fols. 2v-3r: Calendaric note containing feast days of the Evangelists and disciples.</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fols. 2v: ሠረቀ፡ መስከረም፡ አመ፡ ፩በርተሎሜዎስ፡ ሐዋርያ። ሠረቀ፡ ጥቅምት፡ አመ፡ ፩ወሰኑዩ፡ ማቴዎስ፡ ሐዋርያ። አመ፡ ፳ወ፪ሉቃስ፡ ወንጌላዊ፡ ሠረቀ፡ ኅዳር፡ አመ፡ ፲ወ፰ፊልጶስ፡ ሐዋርያ።...</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a4">
                           <locus target="#00">Fols. 3r-3v: Protective prayer (containing ˀasmat?).</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 3r: በቃለ፡ እግዚአብሕር፡ አብ፡ ቆሔት፡ ወልድ፡ ቆሔት፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ቆሔት፡ እንዘ፡ ፫፡ ፩ወእንዘ፡ ፩፫ቱ፡ ጺዱመ፡ ልጋመ፡ እሳት፡ አውላልኤል፡ ኀብዕ፡ መለኮት፡ በዝንቱ፡ አስማቲከ...</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a5">
                           <locus target="#00"/>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 3v: በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፩አምላክ። ጸሎተ፡ ምሕረት፡ መላእክት፡ ወሰማዕት፡ ወጳጳሳት፡ ወቀሳውስት፡ ወሰዲያቆናተ፡ ዘጸለዩ፡ ዘንተ፡ ጸሎተ፡ ብእንተ፡ ዕፁባት፡ አንስት፡ ...</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a6">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#"/>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 4r: በስመ፡ አብ፡ በል፡ ግርሙያል፡ ሽርሙያል፡ አናንያል፡ አዘርያል፡ ተንሥአ፡ ማሰያስ፡ ወሲላሶ፡ እንዘ፡ ይቁረጥም፡ እደ፡ ወእግረ፡ ወኵሉ፡ አባለ፡ ሥጋሁ፡ ለገብርከ፡ ዓምደ፡ ሚካል[sic]፡ ዘዮናስ፡ ዘዮናስ፡ ዘዮናስ፡ እንዘ፡ደቁረጥም፡ እደ፡ ወእግረ፡ ወነፋሱ፡ ለገብርከ፡ ዓምደ፡ ሚካኤል፡</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a7">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#"/>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 4v: ሰላ፡ ለከ፡ ሰዳደ፡ አጋንንት፡ ፋኑኤል፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ እምጽርሑ፡ ከመ፡ ኤይስክዩ፡ ሰብአ፡ እለ፡ ይኔሁ፡ ለጌጋይ፡ዘዘኢአሁ።...</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a8">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#">Fol. 5v-6r: Fragment of an unidentified text.</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a9">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#"/>
                           <q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a10">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#"/>
                           <q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Wäldä ʾAnanya is written in red in a supplication formula over an erasue, on fol. 50rb.&#xD;
- Ethiopic numerals are crudely written in pencil in the upper margins at the beginnings of quires (starting at quire IX): fols. 63r, 71r, 79, 95.&#xD;
- At the incipit page of Text II (fol. 65vb), a directive concerning the use of the text is written in the upper margin: ከለአተ፡ ድግመ፡ ዝንቱ፡ ኢትህድጉ “Do not forget to read this twice”.&#xD;
- Text has been erased on fol. 107r and a cross has been painted over it.</item>
                     </list>
